echosmart-gateway (1.0.0-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial production release
  * CLI with subcommands: run, status, test-sensors, version
  * 5 sensor drivers: DS18B20, DHT22, BH1750, Soil Moisture, MH-Z19C
  * Local SQLite cache for offline resilience
  * MQTT publishing and cloud sync
  * systemd service integration
  * Setup wizard for first-run configuration
  * Debian packaging for Raspberry Pi OS

 -- EchoSmart Team <dev@echosmart.io>  Sat, 29 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000
